  section#research
    h2 The cafes: Lindt cafes have an image problem
    .text-flow-columns
      p Visiting cafes and competitors, observing and surveying customers and staff revealed that the cafe experience was fantastic, but it had a very traditional image, low awareness and narrow target market.

    figure
